when you go home.

289
00:13:42,559 --> 00:13:43,679
Don't drink water that's too hot.

290
00:13:44,120 --> 00:13:44,799
In recent days,

291
00:13:44,959 --> 00:13:45,760
you'd better have

292
00:13:45,880 --> 00:13:47,520
