293
00:13:47,679 --> 00:13:49,199
Don't eat spicy, greasy,

294
00:13:49,360 --> 00:13:50,400
stimulating foods.

295
00:13:51,199 --> 00:13:52,919
Also, avoid strenuous exercise.

296
00:13:53,319 --> 00:13:54,400
Relax and get more rest.

297
00:13:54,679 --> 00:13:55,120
